+/// The static-endpoints gateway client mode: a [`Gateway`] whose chunk plane
+/// fans out over gRPC clients to a *configured* list of D-server endpoints, with
+/// metadata and coordination held locally under a data dir. This is the
+/// user-facing composition the brief calls for — the `wyrd` binary itself is the
